headline: A Fresh Look at Google's (GOOGL) Valuation After Defense AI Deal and New Pixel Launch
summary: Alphabet (GOOGL) has been busy making headlines, and if you’re weighing your next move on the stock, this week’s news definitely raises the stakes. The company just kicked off a significant Department of Defense pilot partnership, bringing the power of Google’s AI and cloud solutions to modern military workflows alongside SMX and World Wide Technology. At the same time, Alphabet unveiled its latest Google Pixel lineup with T-Mobile, now featuring enhanced Gemini AI and satellite connectivity...
